= Internal Factions of the SPD

{!<span class="tooltip-text" title="The Left (Spartacus League) oppose the war and pursue revolution.">Left</span>!} strength: [+ left_strength : strength +], dissent: [+ left_dissent : dissent +]

{!<span class="tooltip-text" title="The Center oppose the war, and wish to pursue an immediate peace.">Center</span>!} strength: [+ center_strength : strength +], dissent: [+ center_dissent : dissent +]

{!<span class="tooltip-text" title="The Right (MSPD) support the war, however would like for it to end sooner rather than later.">Right</span>!} strength: [+ reformist_strength : strength +], dissent: [+ reformist_dissent : dissent +]

